<p>
<p>A researcher first wants to center the predictors in a model before looking at interaction between predictors.</p>
<p>What formula creates a centered variable?</p>
</p>]]></text>
</questiontext>
<generalfeedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
</p>]]></text>
</generalfeedback>
<penalty>0</penalty>
